phase2.explanation:
For `OnTriggerEnter` to work, at least one of the colliders must be a trigger (`isTrigger = true`).

**The fix:**
```csharp
void Start()
{
    Collider2D col = GetComponent<Collider2D>();
    if (col != null)
    {
        col.isTrigger = true;  // ← Enable trigger!
    }
}
```

**Sharp-chan says:**
"Triggers need `isTrigger = true`. Without that, they're just normal colliders."
